org.jgap.distr.grid.gp
Interface IGPPopulationInitializer

All Known Implementing Classes:
GPPopulationInitializer
public interface IGPPopulationInitializer

Allows to initialize a GP population right when creating a GPGenotype. Is called within constructor of GPGenotype. See examples.grid.mathProblemDistrubuted for an example.
